    <description>Plants perennial. Roots single, to 30 × 1–2.5 cm. Leaves: cauline leaves scattered,
        crowded toward end of stems; blade gray-green, grooved or flat adaxially, 15–20 × 0.5–2 cm,
        apex acute, glabrous. Inflorescences: peduncle to 12 cm. Flowers lasting 2–4 days, 5–9 cm
        diam.; petals 200–250, in concentric rows, shining yellow; stamens to 10 mm; ovary
        10–20-loculed. Seeds 75–200, dark brown, 1–1.8 mm, ca. 25% located within paired pockets. 2n
        = 18.</description>
